circuits.qi_Z:
version 3.0

qubit[2] q

// Prepare |01> (Hartree-Fock state)
X q[1]

// UCCSD ansatz
CNOT q[1], q[0]
Ry q[0], 1.441311
CNOT q[1], q[0]

measure q
circuits.qi_X:
version 3.0

qubit[2] q

// Prepare |01> (Hartree-Fock state)
X q[1]

// UCCSD ansatz
CNOT q[1], q[0]
Ry q[0], 1.441311
CNOT q[1], q[0]

// Rotate to X basis
H q[0]
H q[1]

measure q
circuits.qi_Y:
version 3.0

qubit[2] q

// Prepare |01> (Hartree-Fock state)
X q[1]

// UCCSD ansatz
CNOT q[1], q[0]
Ry q[0], 1.441311
CNOT q[1], q[0]

// Rotate to Y basis
Sdag q[0]
H q[0]
Sdag q[1]
H q[1]

measure q
